{"tid":1086754,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞mv現正上線]〈沙墟〉原：龍舌蘭","createTime":"2019-04-01T03:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T07:34:51.000Z","uid":122380,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4535a7ea4137c762d5986422646919a348496dbb","tid":1086754,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"每次聽到龍舌蘭都會諗，<br />\n如果我就係蘇麗珊會點呢？<br />\n如果Eason望住第三者個陣係帶住一絲猶疑<br />\n咁望向我個陣呢？<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQ6y7cmBRcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoQ6y7cmBRcs&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=9879eb04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQ6y7cmBRcs</a><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n原曲：龍舌蘭<br />\n原唱：陳奕迅<br />\n原詞：陳詠謙<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n〈沙墟〉<br />\n主唱：靜香唔沖涼<br />\n改詞：碧落<br />\n混音：翊風<br />\n<br />\n埋下證據 埋在沙礫中的真相 蘊藏著顧慮<br />\n被締取 難像覆水般給蒸發 卻遺下變序<br />\n三方棲身於鳥居 你我似失足再跌墜<br />\n<br />\n你 猶疑地望向我 沙墟足跡烙舊痕 承諾卻飛墮<br />\n相機印證著泛黃  長夜獨對空房<br />\n指尖相抵的感覺  卻未過<br />\n<br />\n難道告吹 誰為沙礫中的真相 悄然亂了序<br />\n三方棲身於廢墟 舌戰過心中各顧慮<br />\n<br />\n你 猶疑地望向我  沙墟足跡換舊人 承諾悄飛墮<br />\n相機印證著泛黃  長夜獨對空房<br />\n指尖相抵的感覺  怎麼似拆遷故地難覓逐過往<br />\n當初親暱 今天卻割裂別說破<br />\n<br />\n我 無餘力再跟你 山崩天覆亦並行 前路遍災禍<br />\n三方葬送在地牢 無力迸發花火<br />\n指尖相抵的感覺  已漸過<br />\n這一鬆手似是 慶賀<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n雖然上次反應麻麻，不過都係搵左人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw原來整首cover真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順手向咁多位連登改詞唱歌後製巴絲們致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b7103fbb618f209f90983a85a0824ef06de153","tid":1086754,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"碧巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c0a4079b70336de1344b2884c4c00087072f78","tid":1086754,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b7103fbb618f209f90983a85a0824ef06de153","tid":1086754,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"碧巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"小魚子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62212fd94cfbe288133c7b333ca4dfc2c46ad541","tid":1086754,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"發覺近排大家都少產左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6f149da53aae7689f9573c8140f46a2ab9ccb5","tid":1086754,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62212fd94cfbe288133c7b333ca4dfc2c46ad541","tid":1086754,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:48:17.000Z","msg":"發覺近排大家都少產左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"我算唔算多產<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c11ba19b4b09f48ce71f72fbcc2448f6f25fde","tid":1086754,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62212fd94cfbe288133c7b333ca4dfc2c46ad541","tid":1086754,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB